{"tid":802788,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"對X JAPAN HIDE既睇法","createTime":"2018-09-01T17:01:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T17:43:18.000Z","uid":204246,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"94f8919aa586acd9934282b45cfbc07500008c5a","tid":802788,"uid":204246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T17:01:13.000Z","msg":"我係X JAPAN年資1年既歌迷,我翻查左好多關於佢地成員既消息,網上同實物既書都有,主要講下比較少人提既野<br />\n大路既就唔講<br />\n以下係我主觀既睇法<br />\nPATA講關於HIDE既野<br />\nHIDE既指法技術好好,從未見過佢出錯,係參與HIDE主導既樂團時,如果團員們無好好練曲會比HIDE動粗,但HIDE好快就會原諒對方,再好好地道歉,會因為一句詞,重錄幾小時<br />\n曾經HIDE同YOSHIKI飲醉衝入電台強行同Toshi做直播節目(當然係亂七八糟)<br />\n-------------------<br />\nTaiji講關於HIDE既野<br />\n未見過HIDE係台上犯錯,PATA都會彈錯或甩碌,HIDE次次都好穩定,飲醉左會變左第二個人,有自毀傾向,*HIDE因為Taiji吸毒既問題,向YOSHIKI提出將Taiji退團提議<br />\n(*日本坊間留流傳Taiji被退團主因,曾有道友稱見過流落街頭既Taiji隊野(可信大但無實證))<br />\nTaiji知道後有幾次因小事借題發揮暴打HIDE<br />\n只有HIDE同Taiji可以左右到YOSHIKI係音樂上既決定(可惜Taiji退團後HIDE已經無咩音樂上強烈意願,一切聽從YOSHIKI意思)<br />\n-------------------<br />\nHIDE本人自述,HIDE係松本秀人自己製造出黎既舞台明星,同本身既性格完全唔同<br />\nI.N.A有問佢PINK SPIDER中既故事係咪寫自己,HIDE無正面答,只係笑笑口帶過話題<br />\nHIDE自言醉後會有時出現自毀傾向,有兩次斷片後嚴重重傷事故,一次撞爆頭,一次跌斷腳<br />\n------------------<br />\nHIDE既死係意外,有雙重人格<br />\n音樂技術係死前已得到<br />\n多名海外神檯級人士贊歎<br />\nHIDE令日本出現大量女性搖滾歌迷<br />\n對於搖滾樂普及既貢獻呢方面係非常驚人<br />\n---------<br />\n最後想分享一下YOSHIKI係自傳中提過既手製貼紙(係公路飛走左一堆個張)<br />\n特典鏡同VANISHING VISION簽名黑膠<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/02/010103_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F02%2F010103_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ffe26300&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"261f63c28a69aaa63be9333185dd30121918250c","tid":802788,"uid":3063,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T17:03:14.000Z","msg":"搵我咩事"},{"pid":"8a673218c838a2e2970d6d26b1884fead4b86aa3","tid":802788,"uid":37431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T17:06:51.000Z","msg":"一年年資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74bb5431c744bb3340b96467e3882e3b9726f49f","tid":802788,"uid":3063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8a673218c838a2e2970d6d26b1884fead4b86aa3","tid":802788,"uid":37431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T17:06:51.000Z","msg":"一年年資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T17:08:19.000Z","msg":"團員用細楷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5220806e0a00ae5d08f1b2b5bcf1a9e16ac7a5c4","tid":802788,"uid":204246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T17:11:34.000Z","msg":"唔記得講，我唔係HIDE粉，但我都好欣賞佢，X入便我最鍾意係Toshi"},{"pid":"8599a90e23ee6df9d44ca0a4cd90ec4a287c5ce6","tid":802788,"uid":52132,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T17:13:36.000Z","msg":"Anyway he is a legend"},{"pid":"d995c72812c3a359ca6ec422c2a752307c314bae","tid":802788,"uid":185513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T17:15:29.000Z","msg":"張VANISHING VISION簽名黑膠你架？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5da05566520907709b5ea7c2febb5b64eea6b123","tid":802788,"uid":204246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d995c72812c3a359ca6ec422c2a752307c314bae","tid":802788,"uid":185513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T17:15:29.000Z","msg":"張VANISHING VISION簽名黑膠你架？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T02:08:05.000Z","msg":"yes。入手價就